title: #92Noon: Nordo in for PA! Russo/Johnson/Gleeman
description: Eric Nordquist is in the big chair today for PA. Starting things off with the Wild's victory from last night. The Athletic's Michael Russo joins to give his take. Some NFL News, is it a 'Big Deal or No Big Deal?' Ron Johnson joins in studio. And wrapping things up with Aaron Gleeman.
